name: David Sven
disclosureNotes: From that artist's website https://www.davidsven.com/about-project: "The voice you hear and the songs you find here were brought to life using modern creative tools — including AI-assisted production — always guided by a human hand and heart. Every lyric is written with intention. Every sound is chosen with care. David may not be a person you can shake hands with. But the feelings in his music are real — and they’re meant for you."
